description.h2: The value of the priority attribute must be strictly less than 10.
description.p: Future standard taxonomy linkbases may need to prevent specific arcs from being prohibited.
REMARK: This only applies to a company extension linkbase. The RR 2010 standard taxonomy linkbase contains links with priority attributes of 10, and is therefore a 'good' test variation.
